(13, 'Deep Learning and Big Data Analytics', '2019-11-02', '2019-11-14', 'A TWO WEEK Faculty Development programme on Deep Learning and Big Data Analytics from 02nd to 14th November 2019. The resource persons are from premier institutions like NITs, IIITs, Universities and reputed Industry. In this regard, we invite you to participate and also encourage your research scholars & faculty members to utilize this opportunity.\nThe registration fee for the FDP course is Rs.1000/- and the registration closes by 26/10/2019. As the maximum seats are limited to forty (40), the participants are selected on first come first serve basis. \nBoarding and lodging will be provided for the participants at free of cost.\nTravelling Allowance (TA) is also reimbursed as per AICTE norms.\n\n \n\nFor your reference FDP broacher and Registration from are attached to this mail. Please send your participation details and filled the Registration form to fdpsrkrec@gmail.com', 'event_details.php?id=13', NULL, NULL, 'IT', '2019-10-22 11:22:52'),
