(42, 'FDP ON RESEARCH (CSE)', '2020-08-03', '2020-08-07', 'Dept of CSE, SRKR Engineering College is organising a national level one week online  FDP on An Academic Perspective on Research from 3rd Aug, 2020 to 7th Aug, 2020. Deadline for registration is 31st July, 2020, 5.00 P.M. Registrations can be done using below link (Website Button Below).<br><br>\r\n\r\nDay1:Problem Identification, Research Design<br>\r\nDay2:Writing Quality Research Paper & Publication Measures<br>\r\nDay3:Research Metrics & Journal, Citation Management tools<br>\r\nDay4:IPR, Patent Writing & Patent Filing Process<br>\r\nDay5:Project Proposal Writing, Funding Opportunities<br><br>\r\n\r\nRegistration is FREE<br><br>\r\n\r\n\r\nFDP dates: 3rd - 7th August, 2020(both days Inclusive)<br> \r\nTimings: 10.00 a.m. to 12.00 p.m                                                                                 \r\n\r\n<br><br>\r\n<b>Note:</b>\r\nE-Certificate will be provided to all the participants upon successful completion of FDP and submission of feedback form.                                                                                           \r\n\r\n<br><br>Brochure: <a href=\'files/CSE/AAPR_Brochure.pdf\' target=\"_new\">Download Brochure</a><br><br> \r\n  \r\nRegistration link: <a href=\'https://forms.gle/giyt9hWtbVvosDfb9\' target=\"_new\">https://forms.gle/giyt9hWtbVvosDfb9</a><br><br>   \r\n\r\nRegistration Deadline:  31st July 2020 by 5.00 PM.<br>\r\nConfirmation by Mail: 2nd August, 2020 by 5.00 PM.<br><br>\r\nFor any queries mail us on : aprcsefdp@gmail.com<br><br>\r\n\r\n<b>Convenor:</b>                                                                                                                                         \r\nDr. M S V S Bhadri Raju,Professor and HOD,CSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                        