(59, 'FDP on Outcome Based Education And NBA Accreditation for TIER-II Colleges', '2021-03-29', '2021-04-03', 'A One-Week Virtual Faculty Development Program under AICTE-MARGDARSHAN SCHEME for Mentor and Mentee Institutions on \"Outcome Based Education And NBA Accreditation for TIER-II Colleges\" is being organized from 29-Mar-21 to 03-April-21 in two sessions per day (Morning Session 10:30 to 11:45 & Afternoon Session 14:00 to 15:15)<br><br>\n\nNo Registration FEE<br><br>\n\nOnline FDP Brochure link:<a href=\'\nhttp://srkrec.ac.in/margadarshan.pdf\' target=\'_new\'>\nhttp://srkrec.ac.in/margadarshan.pdf</a>\n<br><br>\nE-Certificate will be given to all faculty who attended all 6-days sessions<br><br>\n\nFDP - Online link will be provided through Email or Whatsapp group\n\nAll the HODs are requested to intimate their faculty members to attend FDP with out fail.', 'event_details.php?id=59', NULL, NULL, '', '2021-03-28 03:30:00'),
