(62, 'Workshop on Interactive Design in Transportation Geotechnics: Theory to Practice', '2021-05-29', '2021-05-30', 'Department of Civil Engineering (SRKREC), jointly with Cheyutha Student Club and Indian Geotechnical Society Student Chapter, Bhimavaram is organizing a Two day Virtual Workshop on \"Interactive Design in Transportation Geotechnics: Theory to Practice\" during 29th to 30th May 2021, sponsored by AICTE under SPICES scheme, GoV of India.\n\nIt is our immense pleasure to invite you to attend the course. The course will be highly beneficial for the academicians and students.\n\nThe registration is FREE but mandatory (only registered participants will receive the Zoom link to join the sessions).', 'event_details.php?id=62', NULL, NULL, 'CV', '2021-05-27 03:30:00'),
(63, 'CSE FDP on Data Science & Its Applications', '2021-06-10', '2021-06-15', 'Department of Computer Science and Engineering that has completed 30 years of its existence is organizing one-week virtual FDP on \"Data Science and its Applications\" during 10th June to 15th June 2021.<br>\nThrough this FDP, the participants could upgrade their theoretical and practical knowledge in Data Science. The key takeaways include Real time applications of Data science, Case studies in Machine learning, Hands on practice on Pycaret, Data generation using modelling and simulation. We are happy to invite all Faculty Members/Scholars/ PG students of any department/discipline to this virtual FDP.<br><br>\n\n<b>Dates:</b> 10th to 15th June, 2021<br> \n<b>Timings:</b> 2.00 to 4.30 PM\n\n<br><br>E-Certificate will be provided to all the eligible participants upon successful completion of FDP.<br><br> \n\n<b>Registration link:</b> <a href=\'https://tinyurl.com/2hsjmd8p\' target=\"_new\">https://tinyurl.com/2hsjmd8p</a><br>\n<b>Registration Charge:</b> Free<br><br>\n<b>FDP Brochure:</b> <a href=\'files/CSE/fdp_dsa.pdf\' target=\'_new\'>Click Here</a><br><br>\n\n<img src=\'img/events/fdp_dsa.jpg\' width=\'400px\'>\n\n', 'event_details.php?id=63', NULL, NULL, 'CS', '2021-06-03 03:30:00'),
