(67, 'SDL-2021 ', '2021-08-09', '2021-08-14', 'Department of Engineering Mathematics and Humanities of SRKREC is organizing  a One-Week virtual National Faculty Development Program on <b>Scientific Documentation Using LaTeX</b> (SDL-2021).\n<br><br>\n\n<b>FDP Schedule:</b> 09-08-2021 to 14-08-2021<br>\n\n<b>Timings IST:</b>\n Every day @ 02:00 PM to 04:00 PM\n\n<br><br>E-Certificates will be issued to participants who attend and submit the feedback forms of all sessions.\n<br><br>\n<b>Registration is free</b>\n<br><br>\n<b>Registration Link:</b>\n<a href=\'https://forms.gle/BgdNEjqAMBKu55YCA\' target=\'_new\'>https://forms.gle/BgdNEjqAMBKu55YCA</a>\n<br><br>\nMeeting link, Programme schedule and all other updates of FDP will be intimated in Whatsapp Group only. Kindly join in any one of the Whatsapp groups after the registration.                                                                              \n<br><br>\n<b>CONVENOR:</b> \nDr. R. Subba Rao<br>\nProfessor of Mathematics & HOD<br>\n\n<b>Contact details:</b>\nsrkrmathsfdp2021@gmail.com\n<br><b>Phone:</b><br>\n1)+91 8096844888 (Dr.G.N.V.Kishore)<br>\n2)+91 9949157026 (Mrs.G.Santhi)<br>\n3)+91 9866476492 (Sri K.S.Srinivasa Babu)<br>\n4)+91 9949062173 (Sri T.Satish)', 'event_details.php?id=67', NULL, '', 'HS', '2021-08-05 03:30:00'),
