(199, '2022-07-20', '', 'Prize Distribution to Winners of Shuttle Tournament', 'Prizes were distributed to the winners of Shuttle and Badminton tournaments that were conducted at SRKR, on the occasion of 89th Birth Anniversary Celebrations of the founder of SRKR Sri. Sagi Rama Krishnam Raju garu on 19th July, 2022. Speaking on this occasion Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju garu and Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that SRKR was planning to host State and National Level Badminton and Volleyball tournaments in the coming days. SRKR PD Dr. Satyanarayana Raju and team participated in this occasion.<br>\r\n\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/20_july_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20_july_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/20_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/20_july_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20_july_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/20_july_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20_july_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-07-20 04:26:15'),
(200, '2022-07-24', '', 'Eye Medical Camp Conducted at SRKREC', 'SRKR Engineering College Women Empowerment Cell in collaboration with Maxivision had conducted a general Eye Medical Camp at Pedda Amiram village. This camp was inaugurated by the Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju. Speaking on this occasion he said that Technological advancements should be made available to the rural areas too. Unnat Bharat Abhiyan, the flagship programme of central Govt is being followed diligently at SRKR and as a part of this the college had adopted five villages in Kalla Mandal and is creating awareness on Ban of Plastic Items, Providing clean drinking water and many developmental aspects. Nearly 200 patients attended this camp and they were provided with free medicines.<br>\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_july_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_july_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_july_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_july_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_july_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_july_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>', '', '', '2022-07-25 04:26:15'),
(201, '2022-07-24', '', 'SRKR to conduct Workshop on IPR', 'SRKR Engineering College is going to conduct an online workshop on the topic of \'Intellectual\r\nProperty Rights, Patents and Design Filing\' on 25-07-2022, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju\r\nhad said. The poster relating to the same was released by SRKR Vice President Sri. SV Ranga Raju.\r\nProgramme Convener and Dean Academics Dr. Suresh Babu had said that this workshop was being\r\norganised in collaboration with Rajiv Gandhi National Institute of Intellectual Property Management\r\nat Nagpur. The resource person of this workshop would be Mr. Kumar Raju, who was the Assistant\r\nController of Patents and Designs at Mumbai. HOD of Mechanical Dept Dr. Brahma Raju,\r\nCoordinators Dr. Rajesh and Dr. Charan participated in this meeting.<br>\r\n\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_july_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_july_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_july_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_july_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_july_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_july_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', 'ME', '2022-07-25 04:26:15'),
(202, '2022-07-26', '', 'Kargil Vijay Divas Celebrated at SRKREC \r\n', 'SRKR Engg College had celebrated \'Kargil Vijay Diwas\' in a grand manner and donated Rs. 1L to the \'Armed Forces Flag Day Fund\'. The cheque was handed over to the District Sainik Welfare Officer Sri. Prasad Rao by the Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Rangaraju and Principal Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju. NSS In charge Dr. Krishna Chaitanya and Co-Ordinator Mr. Prasada Raju had said that the college faculty and the students donated this amount to the sainik welfare. Speaking on this occasion Principal of SRKR Dr.M.Jagapathi Raju had said that it is the duty of everyone to support the armed forces who are fighting bravely for the country. Everyone paid homage to the martyred soldiers.<br>\r\n\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_5.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_6.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_7.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_7.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>', '', '', '2022-07-27 04:26:15'),
(203, '2022-07-26', '', 'Workshop on NEP conducted at ZP High School, Kopalle', 'SRKR Engg College UBA Cell had conducted an workshop on \'National Educational Policy\' at ZP High School, Kopalle. Prof. R. Subbarao had enlightened the students on NEP and its importance. Dr. Ganesh enlightened on the topic of \'Non-Renewable Energy Sources\' and Dr. Kishore enlightened on the topic of \'Water Resources\'. Village Coordinator Dr. Rambabu, Principal of Kopalle ZP High School Mr. Satyanarayana Murthy, Faculty Mr. Manikyala Rao, Mr. Ravikumar and members of SRKR WET Center participated in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_8.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_8.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/26_july_2022_9.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/26_july_2022_9.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-07-27 04:26:15'),
(205, '2022-07-29', '', 'Awareness Camp Condcted for Pregnant Ladies', 'SRKR College under UBA scheme is going to conduct an awareness camp for the pregnant ladies of the Peda Amiram village. This camp will be attended by the President and Vice-President of the village. This programme was being conducted in collaboration with UBA Women Empowerment Cell, Vasavi Club and Village Panchayat of Peda Amiram. Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, UBA Convener Dr. Ramakrishnam Raju, Women Empowerment Cell Coordinator Dr. Bhuvaneshwari participated in this poster release event.<br>\r\n\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/29_july_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/29_july_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/29_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/29_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/29_july_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/29_july_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-07-30 04:26:15'),
(204, '2022-07-27', '', 'Farmers Meeting on Organic Farming Conducted', 'SRKR Engg College under UBA conducted farmers meet at \'Raithu Bharosa Kendram\', Peda Amiram village. Speaking on this occasion Prof. Ganesh enlightened the farmers on the concept of \'Organic Farming\' so that they can reduce their investment and increase their productivity. He said that the land will lose its fertility because of more fertilizer using. The farmers were distributed with free seeds. Vice President of the village Mr. Kishore, Faculty Dr. Subbarao, Mr. Satyanarayana, Mr. Rambabu participated in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n  <li><a href=\"img/news/27_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/27_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n  <li><a href=\"img/news/27_july_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/27_july_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '2022-07-27 04:26:15'),
(206, '2022-08-01', '', 'Awareness Session by Women Empowerment Cell', 'The Women Empowerment Cell at SRKR Engg College had conducted an Awareness Session on \'Preventive Measures During Emergencies\'. The resource person Dr. Govinda Babu had said that patients can be saved during emergencies by offering them first aid at the right time. Even the organs of the patients during accidents can be saved if they were taken to the medical attention immediately. Everyone should make use of 100, 104 and 108 in case of any medical emergencies. Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that students should give due care to the sports too along with academics so that they would be mentally and physically strong. Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju, Women Empowerment Cell in charge Dr. Lakshmi, Women Empowerment Cell Coordinator Dr. Bhuvaneshwari took part in this session and Dr. Govinda Babu was felicitated for his magnificent inputs.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/1_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/1_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/1_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/1_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-02 04:26:15'),
(207, '2022-08-02', '', 'FDP by CSE Department Inaugurated', 'Department of CSE at SRKR Engg College is conducting an FDP for one week and the same was inaugurated yesterday by Mr. Narasimha from Blackbucks. Speaking on this occasion he urged the students and the faculty to make use of new technology in the academic projects and assignments. He said that making use of the new technologies nearly 90% are getting good job offers in foreign countries and in India it is only 50 to 60%. Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that everyone should adopt latest technologies as per the National Educational Policy. CSE HOD Dr. Chandrasekhar had said that the FDP has got good response and the desire to learn new technologies had been increasing in everyone. Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Rangaraju, Director Dr.Jeevasagar, Co-Ordinators Dr. Someshwara Rao and Dr. Sirisha took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/2_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/2_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/2_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/2_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', 'CS', '2022-08-03 04:26:15'),
(208, '2022-07-28', '', 'Workshop on NEP conducted for School Students', 'SRKR Engg College UBA Cell had conducted an workshop on \'National Educational Policy\' at ZP High School, Kopalle. Prof. R. Subbarao had enlightened the students on NEP and its importance. Dr. Ganesh enlightened on the topic of \'Non-Renewable Energy Sources\' and Dr. Kishore enlightened on the topic of \'Water Resources\'. Village Coordinator Dr. Rambabu, Principal of Kopalle ZP High School Mr. Satyanarayana Murthy, Faculty Mr. Manikyala Rao, Mr. Ravikumar and members of SRKR WET Center participated in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/28_july_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/28_july_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/28_july_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/28_july_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-07-29 04:26:15'),
(209, '2022-08-03', '', 'UBA Programme at Pedamiram Primary School', 'SRKR Engineering College had conducted \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\' at Primary school of Peda Amiram village under UBA Scheme. Speaking on this occasion, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that as we are celebrating 75 years of Indian Independence, everyone should hoist and respect the national flag at their homes and other public places. UBA Coordinator Dr. Ramakrishnam Raju, Faculty Mr. Meher Ganesh, Mr. Subbarao and Head Mistress of School Ms. Padmavathi participated in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/3_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/3_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/3_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/3_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '2022-08-04 04:26:15'),
(210, '2022-08-08', '', 'FDP on Mobile Applications by CSE Dept', 'The Department of CSE at SRKR Engineering College is going to conduct a FDP on \'Mobile Applications\' from 8th to 13th of August, 2022. Speaking on this occasion Principal of SRKR, Dr. Jagapathi Raju had said that faculty should have experience on latest technologies and they should create interest in students to pursue them further. It is because of Android applications that we are getting to know the latest happenings in the world in a few minutes and it is the duty of the faculty to develop further interesting applications and ignite the students. Blackbuck company expert Mr. Narsimha Kanumuri said the faculty and students of SRKR will be benefitted by learning the latest technologies. Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju, CSE In Charge HOD Dr. Mahesh, Prof. Dr. Kameshwara Rao, Assistant Professor Mr. R. Seetharama Raju took part in this occasion.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/8_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/8_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/8_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/8_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/8_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/8_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', 'CS', '2022-08-09 04:26:15'),
(211, '2022-08-10', '', 'FDP on Mobile Applications Concluded \r\n', 'One week FDP on \'Mobile Applications\' by CSE Department had concluded on 10th August, 2022. Speaking on this occasion, Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju had said that it is only through continuous practice and hard work, we can achieve magnificent results. Under the National Education Policy, Research is given utmost importance and hence he suggested the faculty to march ahead in the area of research. Certificates were being distributed to the faculty who had completed the FDP successfully. Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, HOD of CSE Dr. Chandrasekhar, Coordinators Dr. Kameshwara Rao, Mr. Someshwara Rao, G. Sirisha, K. Raghu took part in this function.\r\nFDP by CSE Department Organized.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/10_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/10_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'CS', '2022-08-11 04:26:15'),
(212, '2022-08-10', '', 'National Flag Distribution by SRKR College', 'SRKR Engineering College under the UBA Scheme had distributed National Flags to the students of Kalla ZP High School.  Coordinator Mr. Raghuram had explained to the students about the freedom struggle, national flag and the inspiring story of Mr. Pingali Venkayya.  Faculty of SRKR Mr. Ganesh, Dr. Subbarao, Mr. Jeevan Kumar, Head Mistress of ZP High School, Kalla Ms. Tarakeswari were present in this occasion.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/10_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/10_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '2022-08-11 04:26:15'),
(213, '2022-08-11', '', 'National Flags Distributed', 'SRKR Engineering College under \'UBA\' scheme had distributed National Flag\'s at the Pedda Amiram High School on the occasion of \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\'. UBA Convener Dr. Ganesh, Civil HOD Dr. Prasad, Head Mistress Smt. Prasanna Bharathi took part in this event. Students were asked to remember the sacrifices of the freedom fighters and keep up the spirit of Mother India.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-12 04:26:15'),
(214, '2022-08-11', '', 'War Martyr\'s Families Felicitated', 'SRKR Engineering College in collaboration with NSS Unit and Women Empowerment Cell had felicitated the War Martyr\'s families and the army personnel who were injured in line of duty on 11th August, 2022 on the occasion of \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\'. Speaking on this occasion, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that it is the duty of everyone to recognize the efforts of the martyrs and other army personnel sacrifices. Havaldar A. Trumurthulu, G. Balaji, A. Venkata Lakshmi, U. Anuradha were being felicitated. Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju, Retired Sargent T. Bhogeswara Rao, U. Raju, District Sainik Welfare Officer Mr. Prasada Rao, Dr. P. Bhuvaneshwari, R. Krishna Chaitanya took part in this noble occasion.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_5.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_6.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_7.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/11_aug_2022_7.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '2022-08-12 04:26:15'),
(215, '2022-08-12', '', 'Basketball Competitions on the Occasion of Azadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav', 'SRKR Engineering College Physical Education Department had conducted Basketball competitions on the occasion of \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\' to various colleges in Bhimavaram. Speaking on this occasion, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that sportspersons should show patriotism towards the country along with the sportive spirit. These competitions were being held for two days in which DNR College had emerged as winner in B Team and as runner in A team. Cash Awards, Mementoes and National Flags were being distributed to the players on this occasion. Physical Education Dept Staff Dr. Harimohan, Ms. Sarika, Mr. Ramaraju took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/12_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/12_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-13 04:26:15'),
(216, '2022-08-13', '', 'SRKREC Holds Rally to Celebrate Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav', 'SRKR Engineering college had held a massive rally with 5000 staff and students from college to Alluri Seetharamaraju statue on the occasion of \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\'. Speaking on this occasion SRKR Secretary and Correspondent Sri. SRK Nishanth Varma had said that around 50 hoardings of prominent freedom fighters will be installed in Bhimavaram town on the occasion of 75 Years of Indian Independence. SRKR College in association with Women Empowerment Cell and NSS had been conducting many programmes from the last 10 days in celebrating this jubilant occasion and it is the duty of everyone to remember the sacrifices of the freedom fighters and army personnel in this august moment. Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju, NSS In charge Dr. Krishna Chaitanya, NSS Coordinator Sri. Prasad Raju, staff and students took part in this occasion.<br>\r\n\r\n	<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_5.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_6.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_7.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/13_aug_2022_7.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	 </ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-14 04:26:15'),
(217, '2022-08-15', '', 'Independence Day Celebrations at SRKR', 'The Independence Day Celebrations were conducted in a grand manner at SRKR Engineering College. Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju had hoisted the tricolour with honour and respect.  Speaking on this occasion Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju garu had explained various key moments of the Independence and requested the staff and students to keep up the spirit of Independence alive. Vice-President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju had asked the staff and students to work hard to keep up the pride of the country and institution. The management facilitated the staff and students who had rendered excellent services in their respective fields. Certificates were distributed to the students who excelled in various competitions conducted on the occasion of \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\'.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/15_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/15_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/15_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/15_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	</ul>', '', '', '2022-08-16 04:26:15'),
(218, '2022-08-16', '', 'Scholarships for Students', 'Two SRKR students were given scholarships worth Rs.25000/- instituted in the name of Former Professor Ms. Geetharaj by the 1984-87 batch students. These scholarships were given to the students with good academic record and poor financial status. These scholarships were given to III Year Civil student Ms. Srivallika and III Year ECE student Ms.  Satvika. TTD Annamacharya Project Director Smt. Shobaraj, who was the sister of Late. Geethraj, lauded the efforts of the alumni in giving these scholarships. College Vice President Sri. SV Rangaraju, Principal Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju and representatives of the alumni association participated in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/16_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/16_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/16_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/16_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/16_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/16_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n', '', 'EC', '2022-08-17 04:26:15'),
(219, '2022-08-17', '', 'SRKR Inks MOU with SALCIT Technologies', 'SRKR Engineering College had entered an MOU with Hyderabad based \'SALCIT Technologies Pvt Ltd\' to work mutually on research pertaining to healthcare solutions and consultancy services. The agreement documents regarding the same were mutually exchanged by the Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju and SALCIT Technologies founder CEO Sri. SVN Narayana Rao. Speaking on this occasion, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that Sri. Narayana Rao was an elite alumnus of SRKR and his product was recently inaugurated by PM Modi on the occasion of \'Azaadi Ka Amrit Mahotsav\'. HOD of ECE Dr. Udaykumar had said that Assistant Professors of ECE Dr. Balasindhuri and Venkata Rao with the students of ECE will take this collaborative research ahead.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/17_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/17_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/17_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/17_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'EC', '2022-08-18 04:26:15'),
(220, '2022-08-18', '', 'Merit Scholarship Worth 25K Awarded to Students', 'Merit Scholarships of Rs. 25000 each bestowed in the name of Origanti Sundari were being awarded to ECE Final Year Student Ms. Kusuma and Civil Final Year Student Ms. Saranya by Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju and Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju. Speaking on this occasion Alumni Association Coordinators Dr. Viswanadha Raju and Prof. Subbarao had said that these scholarships were being donated by ECE 1995 batch student and presently the Vice President of Multi Billion Dollars Bank Q2 in US Mr. Origanti Siva Bharat. Civil HOD Dr. Prasad and ECE HOD Dr. Uday Kumar took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/18_aug_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n	 ', '', 'EC', '2022-08-19 04:26:15'),
(221, '2022-08-19', '', 'Mathematics Faculty Receives PhD from JNTUK', 'Mr. S. Ramalingeswara Rao, Assistant Professor in the Dept of Mathematics at SRKR Engineering College had received the PhD degree from JNTUK. Secretary and Correspondent of SRKR, Sri. SRK Nishanth Varma and Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had felicitated him and congratulated him on his achievement.  Mr. Rao had said that he had done his PhD under the guidance of Dr. Deekshitulu from JNTUK and Dr. Vidyasagar from SRKR on the topic of Fluid Dynamics. Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that under the National Educational Policy, it is mandatory for every faculty to have a PhD and urged all the young faculty to complete the PhD at the earliest. HOD of Engineering Mathematics & Humanities Dept, Dr. D. Venkatapathi Raju took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/19_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/19_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/19_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/19_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/19_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/19_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'HS', '2022-08-20 04:26:15'),
(222, '2022-08-20', '', 'PhD Awarded to CSE Faculty', 'Ms. K. Aruna Kumari, Assistant Professor in the Dept of CSE had received her Doctorate Degree from KL University in the field of Cloud Computing. SRKR Secretary & Correspondent Sri. SRK Nishanth Varma and Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had felicitated her on this achievement and wished her all the best for the future endeavours. On this occasion, the management had urged all the young faculty to pursue their research for the benefit of the institution and the society.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/21_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/21_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/21_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/21_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/21_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/21_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'CS', '2022-08-22 04:26:15'),
(223, '2022-08-22', '', 'Merit Scholarship to ECE Student', 'Merit Scholarship of Rs.10000 was being distributed to ECE student Mr. A. Sri Harsha Vamsi by Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju and Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju. This scholarship was being given by the 2003-07 batch ECE students in remembrance of their friend. This scholarship would be given to the male student who stood first until the end of III Year in ECE branch. HOD of ECE Dr. Udaykumar took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'EC', '2022-08-23 04:26:15'),
(224, '2022-08-23', '', 'SRKR Inks MOU with MSME', 'SRKR Engineering college had inked MOU with Visakhapatnam based Govt of India sponsored MSME Technologies in the areas of Engineering Students Projects and study of latest technologies. The deliberations regarding the same happened at SRKR Engineering college and the documents were exchanged between both the institutes. SRKR Secretary & Correspondent Sri. SRK Nishanth Varma, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju and Governing Body Member of SRKR Sri. Pratik Varma, MSME Technologies Deputy GM Sri. G. Prasad Reddy mutually exchanged the documents. Training and Placement Cell Dean Dr. Satyanarayana and others took part in this programme.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/23_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/23_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-24 04:26:15'),
(225, '2022-08-24', '', 'Sagi Atchutarama Raju Gold Medal Awarded to Principal of SRKREC', 'SRKR Principal, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had been awarded with Sagi Achyutarama Raju Gold Medal for his exemplary work on research and expansion in research work. This medal is being awarded to him by Research Advisor and Visiting Professor Dr. Prasada Raju at a conference in the college on \'Research Expansion\'. This medal is being given by SRKR Vice President Sri. SV Ranga Raju in the name of SRKR Co-Founder Sagi Achyutarama Raju for the faculty of SRKR who had tremendously performed in the field of research every year. SRKR Governing Council Member Sri. Pratik Varma and other faculty took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_5.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/24_aug_2022_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-25 04:26:15'),
(226, '2022-08-29', '', 'National Sports Day Celebrated', 'National Sports Day Celebrations were held in a grand manner at SRKR Engineering College and various sports events such as Volley Ball and Running competitions were held and prizes were distributed to the winners by the Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju. Speaking on this occasion, he said that sports will increase self-confidence and zeal through which students may further advance in studies. Physical Education Dept Staff Dr. Satyanarayana Raju, Sri. Harimohan, Smt. Sarika, Volleyball Coach Sri. Ramaraju took part in this event.<br>\r\n	\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/29_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/29_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/29_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/29_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-30 04:26:15'),
(227, '2022-08-22', '', 'Free Dental Camp at Chinna Amiram Village', 'SRKR Engineering College in collaboration with Women Empowerment Cell and Vishnu Dental College had conducted Free Dental Camp at Pedda Amiram Village under the \'Unnat Bharat Abhiyan\' scheme. Speaking on this occasion SRKR Governing Council Member Mr. Pratik Varma had said that SRKR is committed to serve the rural areas with the latest technologies and developments and dedicated to uplift them. Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that as per the directions of PM Modi under \'UBA\' scheme, SRKR is dedicating itself to the upliftment of the rural areas. UBA Cell Convener Dr. Ramakrishnam Raju, UBA Cell Coordinator Dr. Ganesh, Women Empowerment Cell Convener Dr. Lakshmi, President and Vice-President Pedda Amiram Panchayat took part in this noble event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/22_aug_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-08-23 04:26:15'),
(228, '2022-08-30', '', 'SRKR Emerges as Winners in Smart India Hackathon 2022', 'SRKR Engineering College had emerged as the winner in the National Level \'Smart India Hackathon\' and received a cash prize of Rs. 1,00,000. This hackathon was conducted under the aegis of AICTE and HRD Ministry at Pune. College students M. Ganesh Babu, P. Pranav Tej, KNV Goutham, Charan Sai, K. Hema Sai Praneeth and G. Aiswarya had developed a web portal and brought accolades to the institution. College students V. Swetha, P Kusuma, P. Manya Sree, Harshavardhan Nayudu, Kishore Kumar, U. Satya Sai had developed a web portal to solve the problems that arises while charging the electric vehicles and stood second at the hackathon conducted at Manipal University, Jaipur. \r\nSRKR Engg College Secretary and Correspondent Sri. SRK Nishanth Varma, Governing Council Member Sri. Pratik Varma, Vice President Sri. SV Ranga Raju, Principal Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, Heads of various Departments had felicitated both the teams for their outstanding victory. <br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_5.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/30_aug_2022_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'TC', '2022-08-31 04:26:15'),
(229, '2022-09-04', '', 'Lakshmi Ganapati Homam Performed at Campus', 'Lakshmi Ganapati Homam was being performed at the college premises on the occasion of \'Vinayaka Chavithi Celebrations\'.  SRKR Vice President Sri. SV Ranga Raju and Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju along with the large number of staff and students took part in this event. Speaking on this occasion Vice-President and Principal had said that the college will raise to new heights with the divine blessings of the almighty and co-operation of the staff and splendid performance by the students.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/4_sep_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/4_sep_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/4_sep_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/4_sep_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '2022-09-05 04:26:15'),
(230, '2022-09-06', '', 'Competitions on National Education Policy by SRKR NSS Unit', 'The NSS Unit at SRKR Engg College had created awareness session on \'National Education Policy\' and conducted various competitions on the same at Jhansi Lakshmi Bai Municipal Girls High School, Bhimavaram and certificates were distributed to the meritorious students. Speaking on this occasion, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that students should start focussing on skill development right from the early stages of their career. NSS Coordinator Dr. Krishna Chaitanya had created awareness to the students on National Education Policy. School Principal P. Srinivasarao took part in this occasion.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/6_sep_2022_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>', '', '', '2022-09-07 04:26:15'),
(231, '2022-09-07', '', 'Alluri Movie Team Visits SRKR', 'Upcoming Tollywood movie \'ALLURI\' team had visited SRKR college for promotions. Movie hero Sri Vishnu had said that this movie is a message oriented movie and they are very fortunate to shoot the movie in the place where the prominent freedom fighter Alluri Seetharamaraju had born. The college management had felicitated the movie team and wished them all the success ahead. This movie is scheduled to release on 23rd of September. SRKR Vice President Sri. SV Rangaraju, Principal Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, HOD\'s of various departments, Deans and large number of students took part in this event.<br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/7_sep_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/7_sep_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/7_sep_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/7_sep_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/7_sep_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/7_sep_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', '', '2022-09-08 04:26:15'),
(232, '2022-09-08', '', '3 Months Training on R Language Concluded', 'The research centre of Mathematics Dept at SRKR Engg College had conducted 3 months training on \'Mathematics and Statistics Applications in R Language\' to BV Raju Degree college students and certificates were distributed to the students who completed the same successfully by SRKR Vice President Sri. SV Ranga Raju. Speaking on this occasion Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that the research centres at SRKR are developed in such a way that they are beneficial to the students as well as the researchers. He said that the college is having research centres in Mathematics and Physics departments and urged the students and faculty to make use of the same. This training is conducted as a part of the MOU between SRKR and BV Raju College which was inked in 2020. HOD of Mathematics&Humanities Dept Dr. D. Venkatapathi Raju, Programme Coordinator Dr. R. Subbarao, BV Raju Degree College Mathematics HOD Dr. K. Narayana Raju, Assistant Professors Mr. Srinivas and Mr. Satyanarayana took part in this event. <br>\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\">\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/8_sep_2022_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/8_sep_2022_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/8_sep_2022_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/8_sep_2022_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n	  <li><a href=\"img/news/8_sep_2022_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/8_sep_2022_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '', 'HS', '2022-09-09 04:26:15'),
(233, '2022-09-10', NULL, 'Ganesh Nimmajanam Celebrations At SRKR', 'Lord Ganesha Nimmajanam celebrations were held in a grand manner at SRKR Engineering College. Inspite of heavy rains, the celebrations took place in grandeur with the vast number of students and faculty being attended. Ganapati Homam was being conducted in a divine manner by Vice-President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju. The laddus (Prasada) were being distributed to the devotees. Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, HOD√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s, Deans, Staff Members and Students were present in a large number.\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918210232_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918210232_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918210232_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918210232_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918210232_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918210232_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918210232_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918210232_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', '', '2022-09-18 15:32:32'),
(234, '2022-09-15', NULL, 'Engineer\'s Day Celebrated at SRKREC', 'The Engineers day has been celebrated in a grand manner at SRKR Engineering College in collaboration with Institution of Engineers, Bhimavaram Local Centre and Civil Engineering Department. R&B District Engineer Mr. Lokeswara Rao was being felicitated and honoured on this occasion by Vice President of SRKR Sri SV Ranga Raju. Speaking on this occasion, Mr. Lokeswara Rao had said that Engineers play a key role in the development of Nation and makes sure that the nation marches ahead in the path of development. Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said that the former students of SRKR are today playing a vital role in the construction of Polavaram Project, Mission Bhageeradha etc. and are in prominent positions across the globe. R&B Deputy EE PV Ramaraju, AE\'s K. Srihari, M. Srinivas Yadav, K. Pratyusha, RVR Pavan were also being felicitated by the management.  Institution of Engineers National Council Member and HOD of Mechanical Dept, Dr. K. Brahma Raju, IEI Bhimavaram Local Centre Secretary Dr. Suresh Babu, Civil Engineering HOD Dr. Prasad, Civil Engg Professor V. Ramaraju along with staff and students attended this programme. \r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918214234_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214234_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918214234_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214234_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918214234_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214234_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', '', '2022-09-18 16:12:34'),
(235, '2022-09-16', NULL, 'Prominent Alumni Visits Campus', 'Prominent alumni of SRKR and Chairman of Digital Economy Mission of Karnataka Mr. BV Naidu had visited the college and addressed the staff and the students. He suggested the students to pursue research on the problems pertaining to aquaculture like water temperature, feed, pond conditions etc. He examined various projects that re being done by the students in the technology centre and Idea Lab in the college. He said that it would be really feasible if flexibility is there between the start-up founder and start-up user. He said that National Educational Policy will be a revolutionary step towards reforming education sector in India. He was grandly felicitated by the Vice President of SRKR, Sri. SV Ranga Raju, Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju and Governing Council Member Mr. Pratik Varma. \r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918214520_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214520_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918214520_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214520_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', '', '2022-09-18 16:15:20'),
(236, '2022-09-17', NULL, 'Workshop on Gender Senitisation Conducted', 'Women Empowerment Cell in Collaboration with Civil Department had conducted a workshop on \'Gender Sensitization\'. JNTU Senate Council Member Dr. D. Vijayalakshmi has attended this workshop as a chief guest and she said that there will not be discrimination in youth when they are completely involved in chasing their goals and respect towards the society. Everyone should be mentally strong and march ahead in reaching their goals. JNTU Women Empowerment Cell Director Dr. Swaroopa Rani said that it is very happy to see the women empowerment Cell performing exceptionally well at SRKR. Dr. BHVN Lakshmi had presided over this workshop and Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, Dr. P. Ramakrishnam Raju, Dr. Prasad and Dr. Bhuvaneshwari took part in this workshop.\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20220918214719_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214719_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', '', '2022-09-18 16:17:19'),
(237, '2022-09-17', NULL, 'SRKREC Received Times Group Award', 'SRKR Engineering College had received ÀúTimes Group Awards-2022√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢ in the field of \'Excellence in Holistic Education for Next Generation\'. Speaking on this achievement SRKR Vice President Sri. SV Ranga Raju had said that this proud achievement had been bestowed on SRKR for its exemplary contribution in the areas of Societal Development, Educational Excellence and Empowering the students in various sectors. This award had been received by the Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju at Vijayawada on behalf of the institution. The management of the college had felicitated the Principal on this occasion.\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"20220918214944_1. 17th Times Ph3.JPG\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214944_1. 17th Times Ph3.JPG\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"20220918214944_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214944_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"20220918214944_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214944_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"20220918214944_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214944_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"20220918214944_5.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220918214944_5.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', '', '2022-09-18 16:19:45'),
(238, '2022-09-19', NULL, 'DST FDP on Integrative Research in Various Fields of Engineering', 'SRKR Engineering College is conducting a FDP on \'Integrative Research in Various Fields of Engineering\' from 21st to 27th of Sept, 2022 in association with GITAMS University, Principal of SRKR Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju had said.  The brochure relating to the same was inaugurated by SRKR Vice President Mr. SV Ranga Raju. Speaking on this occasion, Technology Centre Head Dr. Gopalakrishna Murthy had said that this FDP would concentrate on various techniques and methods used in projects relating to DST and other funded agencies. HOD of Mechanical Dept, Dr. Brahma Raju would act as Convener, Dr. Gopalakrishna Murthy would be the Coordinator, Dr. Suresh Babu would be the Co-Coordinator and Mr. Pavan Kumar would be the Organizing Secretary for this FDP. \r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20220920145011_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220920145011_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', 'TC', '2022-09-20 09:20:11'),
(239, '2022-09-19', NULL, 'SRKR to Host AP Sub Junior Under 13 Badminton Championship', 'SRKR Engineering College would be hosting the prestigious AP State Sub Junior Under-13 Badminton Championship from 22nd to 25th of this month said Principal of SRKR, Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju. The poster relating to the same was unveiled in the campus by Vice President of SRKR, Sri. SV Ranga Raju. SRKR Governing Council Member Mr. Pratik Varma, District Badminton Association President Smt. Chitturi Usharani, Secretary Mr. Mentee Vamsi Krishna, PD Dr. P. Satyanarayana Raju took part in this programme.\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20220920145327_1.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220920145327_1.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220920145327_2.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220920145327_2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220920145327_3.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220920145327_3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20220920145327_4.jpg\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20220920145327_4.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', 'PE', '2022-09-20 09:23:27');
