(299, '2023-02-13', NULL, 'Valedictory Function Of Hackthon  And Bootcamp', 'The valedictory function of 24 hours Hackathon and 5 Day Bootcamp by the Dept of IT was held on 12 th Feb, 2023. President of SRKR Sri. S. Prasad Raju, Secretary &amp; Correspondent Sri. SRK Nishanth Varma, Vice President of SRKR Sri. SV Ranga Raju, Principal Dr. M. Jagapathi Raju, CEO of Brain O Vision Sri. Naga Ganesh, HOD of IT Dr. BHVSRK Raju took part in this occasion and distributed the prizes to the winners. 1 st Prize in Hackathon was won by the SRKR Team for developing a new E- Commerce system with nominal cost and effective performance. Students from various colleges across the country took part in this event. Event Coordinators Dr. Hemalatha and Dr. Kishore Raju took part in this event.\n\n<ul class=\"gallery-list\"><li><a href=\"img/news/20230216143848_1.png\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20230216143848_1.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20230216143848_2.png\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20230216143848_2.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20230216143848_3.png\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20230216143848_3.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li><a href=\"img/news/20230216143848_4.png\" class=\"image-popup\"><img src=\"img/news/20230216143848_4.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li></ul>', '', 'IT', '2023-02-16 09:08:48'),
